Title: Large distance asymptotic behavior of the emptiness formation

probability of the XXZ spin-1/2 Heisenberg chainAuthors: N. Kitanine, J. M. Maillet, N. A. Slavnov, V. Terras

Comments: LPENSL-TH-10, 8 pages

Journal-ref: J.Phys. A35 (2002) L753-10502

Using its multiple integral representation, we compute the large distanceasymptotic behavior of the emptiness formation probability of the XXZ spin-1/2Heisenberg chain in the massless regime.